rom time to time, which shall be deemed to be incorporated in these T&Cs by reference, at all times and unconditionally.</p><p>Fingo Shop shall have the sole authority to add, change, modify or remove these T&Cs or any of its policies relating to the provisions of Services and (or) Indirect Services n the Fingo Shop Platform, at any time, without prior written notice of intimation. It is hereby clarified that a user shall be responsible for reviewing the T&Cs and policies on the Fingo Shop Platform periodically and keep one's self updated.</p><p>The Services and Indirect Services on the Fingo Shop Platform are only available to users who are competent to enter into legally binding contracts under the Indian Contract Act 1872. Any user who shall be considered incompetent to contract as per the provisions of the Indian Contract Act, 1872, are not eligible to use Fingo Shop Platform, including minors and un-discharged insolvents. Any person using Services and (or) Indirect Services on behalf of a company / firm / partnership / proprietor, represents and warrants that it is duly authorised to accept the T&Cs and the Policies by the user and that such person has the authority to bind the user to these T&Cs and the policies.</p><p>Fingo Shop Platform is a platform provided by Fingo Shop for its users to list their products and to buy other products listed on it by various registered users. It is hereby clarified that Fingo Shop is not a party to any transaction between the users (Buyers and Sellers) of the Fingo Shop Platform and shall not be responsible in any manner, whatsoever, for any representations made by a user on the platform.</p><h3>Listing on the Fingo Shop Platform</h3><p>Fingo Shop provides users with the Fingo Shop Platform to display and showcase merchandise / tangible products manufactured and (or) distributed by the users, and intangible products such as digital content through various media including, but not limited to, audio content, video content, games, etc., (Products) distributed by third parties and for sale and purchase by other users ordering and buying the Products on the Fingo Shop Platform. Fingo Shop shall also provide such other Services as may be included and modified by Fingo Shop from time to time. Fingo Shop may charge a user selling the products, for Services and (or) Indirect Services rendered from time to time. The fees payable by a user selling the products, may include, listing fees, evaluation fees, commission on the product sold, transaction processing fees, integration fees, any other fees as may be levied from time to time in connection with the Services and (or) Indirect Services availed by such user. The Services and Indirect Services are governed by these T&Cs and all applicable Policies of the Fingo Shop Platform, as may be amended from time to time and shall be deemed to be incorporated in these Terms and Conditions by way of reference. Unless expressly stated otherwise, any new features that augment or enhance the current Services and (or) Indirect Services shall be subject to these T&Cs.</p><p>In addition to providing a platform to the users for listing the Products on the Fingo Shop Platform, Fingo Shop shall from time to time provide additional Services including setting up e-commerce platforms or web platforms for users to directly display and showcase its Products, create advertising space wherein users can advertise their Products (Indirect Services). The list of Indirect Services may be amended and modified by Fingo Shop from time to time at its own discretion and option. The user hereby agrees and undertakes that such Indirect Services may be offered by Fingo Shop from time to time at such additional charge. The Seller shall on its own provide all relevant material and price information/deals and offers related to the Products to Fingo Shop for including the said information and details on the Fingo Shop Platform. All such information shall be provided to Fingo Shop at least